724213f-a.title: Manhattan: Washington Street - Jane Street
724213f-a.text:
Washington Street, north from south of Jane Street. A section of the future elevated roadbed for freight trains has already been built on the west side of the street from Horatio to dansevoort Streets, where a warehouse is to be built over it.
March 12, 1933.
P. L. Sperr.
